MILEAGE MONDAY SAMPLE

Warm Up: 300 free + 100 pull

Build Set:
6 x 100 free on 1:45 (descend 1-3, 4-6)

Main Set:
20 x 100 free on 1:40 (hold CSS pace)
200 easy
10 x 100 free on 1:35 (slightly faster than CSS)

Cool Down: 100 free

Total: 3500m

NOTES: Focus on consistent pacing. Use pull buoy for pull sets.

IM WEDNESDAY SAMPLE

Warm Up: 300 free + 100 pull

Build Set:
4 x 50 (25 drill/25 swim) each stroke
4 x 75 IM order on 1:30

Main Set:
8 x 100 IM on 2:00
200 easy
4 x 200 IM on 3:45

Cool Down: 100 free

Total: 2800m

NOTES: Focus on stroke technique. Use fins for fly if needed.

FAST FRIDAY SAMPLE

Warm Up: 300 free + 100 pull

Build Set:
8 x 50 free on 1:00 (build each 50)

Main Set:
10 x 100 free on 2:00 (FAST - race pace)
200 easy
20 x 50 free on 1:00 (FAST)

Cool Down: 100 free

Total: 2700m

NOTES: Full recovery between fast efforts. Focus on technique at speed.

KITCHEN SINK SATURDAY SAMPLE

Warm Up: 300 free + 100 pull

Build Set:
200 kick with board
4 x 75 (25 back/25 breast/25 free) on 1:30

Main Set:
5 x 200 on 3:30 (50 kick/150 swim)
300 pull with buoy
10 x 100 on 1:50 (odds: IM, evens: free)

Cool Down: 100 free

Total: 3100m

NOTES: Mixed session combining all elements. Use various equipment.
